strings:
<voice_0x010015D1><se_high>Jessica: I, I just got this strange image in my head.
There was a desert...and a huge skeleton...
of a dragon, was it? And a crystal ball...

<voice_0x010015D2><se_low>Yangus: That'll be that Dragon Graveyard place
in the desert. South of Argonia, weren't it?
We should get down there, pronto!
<voice_0x010015D3><se_high>Jessica: Ugh, no, I don't like it. It feels too much like when I was being controlled by Rhapthorne.
<voice_0x010015D4><se_low>King Trode: Nonsense! We would be nitwits to ignore such an obvious message. Let us make immediate preparations to depart for the desert!
<voice_0x010015D5><se_low>Yangus: The Dragon Graveyard's a fair old way to the west of 'ere, right? Lucky we can fly, eh!?
